#include <iostream>
#include<string>
#include<algorithm>
using namespace std;
int a[10]={0};
int getpos(int);
int main()
{
    string s[]={"Dhaval", "Shivang", "Bhardwaj", "Rishab", "Maji", "Gaurav", "Dhruv", "Nikhil", "Rohan", "Ketan"};
    int b[10]={0};
    for(int i=0;i<10;i++)
    {
        cin>>a[i];
        b[i]=a[i];
    }
    sort(b,b+10);
    int x,y,z,k;
    for(int i=9;i>=5;i--)
    {
        x = b[i];
        y=getpos(x);
        cout<<s[y]<<endl;
        z=b[9-i];
        k=getpos(z);
        cout<<s[k]<<endl;
    }
    return 0;
}
inline int getpos(int x)
{
    for(int i=0;i<10;i++)
    {
        if(x==a[i])
        {
            a[i]=-1;
            return i;
        }
    }
}
